data.description: This two story traditional home in the Northwest Park neighborhood features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths.  The home was renovated since 2019.  Laminate wood flooring upstairs. Outdoor has been painted.  New AC 2020, roof replaced on 2019 and water heater replaced on Feb 2023; Water softener not working. All bedrooms are upstairs with a nice size family room upstairs.  Backyard is ready for entertaining with a recently installed back patio roof with metal posts.  Come and See!
